                               style=\"margin-top: 50px; padding-top: 35px; border-top: 1px solid #d0d0d0;\">\n                                                <p class=\"body-text\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n                                                    With Distinguished Regards,\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p class=\"body-text\" style=\"font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 5px;\">\n                                                <p style=\"color: blue;\">From </p>\n                                                Prof. Dr. Durba Bhattacharya\n                                                </p>\n                                                <p\n                                                    style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', sans-serif; font-size: 14px; color: #666666; margin: 0;\">\n                                                    Head of the Department of Data Science<br>\n                                                    St. Xavier\'s College (Autonomous), Kolkata\n                                                    <br>\n                                                </p>\n                                            </div>\n\n                                            <!-- Mobile Quick Sections (Shows only on mobile at bottom of main content) -->\n                                            <div class=\"mobile-only\"\n                                                style=\"margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;\">\n                                                <h3 class=\"sidebar-section-title\">\n                                                    <span class=\"sidebar-tab\">Quick Sections</span>\n                                                </h3>\n                                                <a href=\"#\" class=\"sidebar-link\">About St. Xavier\'s College</a>\n                                 